<p>四川九寨沟，旅人的梦想之处。川西高原，蓝天白云，但最美的还是看水。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//f80f/f80f769f4044fd1e4532f4568306b8e0.com/large/19f30006a0473fdf7411"></p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//34af/34afbba347998cde26e03ef666e40723.com/large/19f90000c8b68431e3c7"></p> 
<p>九寨沟属于高原湖泊，不仅干净，还有一种特有的颜色”九寨蓝“。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//650e/650e22bc92ac3741e66e4951aea2a719.com/large/19260006a64c85539c85"></p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//7164/716407985dd646fb064f0c9c32da1bda.com/large/19260006a64d0fb9732a"></p> 
<p>什么季节九寨沟最美?当然是秋季。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//7c99/7c996e516c6f02e20ad64903e64f1149.com/large/19ef0006aeebbdc842fd"></p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//d860/d860389d6c731aafacb7f78f39b88f21.com/large/19f40000d4b19a04f538"></p> 
<p>秋季可以看到金黄色的九寨，品阳光下的灿烂。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//7a4d/7a4d94eb8d6259201869e299f95c7118.com/large/19f30006a04854a8d085"></p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//3836/38366f556561611d91490b654386b77f.com/large/19f90000c8b7328887df"></p> 
<p>可我却选择了夏季来九寨。看到了满目葱绿，有生机却没有明媚秋高气爽。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//b871/b8716f78df8e8ef346b16da6cdbccf52.com/large/19f30006a0497b9c405e"></p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//f77e/f77eeb2fc28ce6fb8f98b496e46f30a1.com/large/19ec0006ba35dfa4939b"></p> 
<p>好在有水。我到九寨就看水！</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//ae8a/ae8a7cf033f2178f52590b7ddf7b6567.com/large/19f30006a04df587a451"></p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//f454/f45498c8872a12e103fcc18f44051482.com/large/19f30006a04b43c02054"></p> 
<p>不仅看很快痴迷于九寨的水。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//6fa3/6fa36d7cec9d3147daa729fffa3fa1cc.com/large/19f90000c8b870acffe9"></p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//5bb0/5bb09528399a32af7fdfec99423185bc.com/large/19f000069714f2d5be37"></p> 
<p>九寨沟的水有静态之美，也有舞动之魂。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//834e/834e3c84fa254da0cd31180bbe3ae0aa.com/large/19f30006a04c772db6b2"></p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//78f1/78f1674505fde71a4369a2bf0891cf02.com/large/19ec0006ba3625c94f51"></p> 
<p>既有一泻千里的干脆，也有生命的不舍与缠绵。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//afea/afea98d94dea4c49ed156f25918b52ba.com/large/19ec0006ba3787ef9610"></p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//ce5d/ce5d64ad238ccc6e86ae90950500310f.com/large/19f40000d4b31cb7cb31"></p> 
<p>而它静止又是你们淡然而透明，仿佛把心掏给你看。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//a577/a57797086ffdfb79cf7934282bb6c8f6.com/large/19ec0006ba381f18b9fd"></p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//5c17/5c17b8803c3a7a89c2f76d2389e768a4.com/large/19f30006a04e249f6c30"></p> 
<p>九寨的水是有魂的！</p> 
